cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.DL, cs.CYBER, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the structure of global research collaboration networks and partnerships among the ASEAN6 countries. 
- cs.SOC (Social and Economic Networks) is also a likely category as the paper examines the collaboration styles of major collaborating countries and their influence on the ASEAN6 countries. 
- cs.DL (Digital Libraries) is a possible category as the paper discusses the production of knowledge in the leading specialisations of the ASEAN6 countries. 
- cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity and Privacy) is a possible category as the paper may touch upon the security and privacy concerns related to international research collaborations. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper may discuss the retrieval and analysis of data related to international research collaborations.
